gobblin.hive

Class HiveTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.hive.HiveRegistrationUnit
      • gobblin.hive.HiveTable

  • @Alpha
public class HiveTable
extends HiveRegistrationUnit
    A class that represents a Hive table.

    This class is used in HiveSpec instead of Hive's Table class to minimize the dependency on the hive-metastore API (since it is unstable and may go through backward incompatible changes). HiveTable and Hive's Table can be converted to each other using HiveMetaStoreUtils.
